Lyrid
=====

|PyPi Version| |Supported Python Versions| |License|

Overview
========

An actor model framework that simplifies concurrent system while support
real parallelism.

No thread/process/async/await, just actor. Implemented in pure Python.â€™

Requirements
============

-  Python 3.8+
-  Works on Linux, Windows, macOS, BSD

Installation
============

using pip:

::

   pip install lyrid

